# Run SAP CAPM APP BUILDER - Full App Launch & Test

## 1. Start Backend Server
- [ ] Activate Python virtual environment
- [ ] Start FastAPI backend (`python -m backend.main`)
- [ ] Verify health endpoint at `http://localhost:8000/api/health`

## 2. Start Frontend Server
- [ ] Install/verify npm dependencies
- [ ] Start Next.js dev server (`npm run dev`)
- [ ] Verify frontend at `http://localhost:3000`

## 3. End-to-End Walkthrough (Browser Test)
- [ ] Visit landing page at `http://localhost:3000`
- [ ] Navigate to Builder wizard at `/builder`
- [ ] Step 0: Create project (name, namespace, description, LLM provider)
- [ ] Step 1: Select a domain template (e.g., E-Commerce)
- [ ] Step 2: Verify/modify entities
- [ ] Step 3-5: Configure services, UI theme, security
- [ ] Step 6: Review AI-generated implementation plan
- [ ] Step 7: Trigger generation and monitor agent progress
- [ ] Step 8: Verify artifacts, preview, and download

## 4. Fix Issues Found During Testing
- [ ] Fix any backend startup errors
- [ ] Fix any frontend build/runtime errors
- [ ] Fix any API communication issues

## 5. Create Walkthrough Documentation
- [ ] Document the full end-to-end flow with screenshots
